caption.p: The effects of 0.5 mg/mL Cymbopogon citratus essential oil and fungicides (25 g/L difenoconazole plus 25 g/L fludioxonil) on seedling emergence. Control, seeds immersed in 0.1% Tween 20. Data are means ± standard error ( n = 5; 10 seeds/treatment). Means with different letters are significantly different ( p ≤ 0.05; Fisher’s LSD tests).
